    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行将很快启动政策战略评估</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-to-launch-policy-strategy-assessment-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行将“很快”开始研究其货币政策策略，预计将在明年下半年得出结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-to-launch-policy-strategy-assessment-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:54:16 GMT</pubDate>
